    <h2>Courier Beta Bug reports</h2>
    <img src="/umbraco/dashboard/images/logo32x32.png" alt="Umbraco" class="dashboardIcon" />
    <h3>
        If you encounter anything that doesn't work as expected, please let us know</h3>
